## Composable Organization

### Feature Structure
```
feature/myfeature/src/main/java/com/shodo/android/myfeature/
├── MyFeatureActivity.kt          # Entry point
├── MyFeatureScreen.kt            # Container (state management)
├── MyFeatureViewModel.kt
├── ui/
│   ├── MyFeatureView.kt          # Main stateless view
│   ├── MyFeatureContent.kt       # Content sections
│   ├── MyFeatureTopBar.kt        # AppBar
│   ├── MyFeatureCard.kt          # Reusable card component
│   └── MyFeaturePreview.kt       # Preview composables
├── uimodel/
│   ├── MyFeatureUI.kt            # UI data models
│   └── UserActionUI.kt           # User action types
├── di/
│   └── MyFeatureModule.kt        # Koin bindings
└── navigator/
    └── MyFeatureNavigatorImpl.kt  # Cross-feature navigation
```

### Composable Naming
- `*View` - Main stateless views
- `*Content` - Content sections within a view
- `*TopBar` - App bar composables
- `*Card` - Card components
- `*Button` - Custom button variants
- `*Preview` - Preview composables (often in separate file)
- `*Item` - List item composables

