## Theme & Styling

### Always Wrap in PokeManiacTheme
In Activity:
```kotlin
class MyFeatureActivity : AppCompatActivity() {
    override fun onCreate(savedInstanceState: Bundle?) {
        super.onCreate(savedInstanceState)
        setContent {
            PokeManiacTheme {
                MyFeatureScreen()
            }
        }
    }
}
```

### Use Material3 Components
```kotlin
// ✅ GOOD
Button(onClick = {}) {
    Text("Click me")
}

FilledTonalButton(onClick = {}) {
    Text("Tonal")
}

// ❌ AVOID custom button wrappers unless truly necessary
```

### SharedCompose Colors & Spacing
Access via `PokeManiacTheme`:
```kotlin
Text(
    text = "Title",
    color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onBackground,
    fontSize = MaterialTheme.typography.headlineSmall.fontSize
)
```

